data.description: Beautiful Shorecrest community home sitting right next to the community garden, park, pool and clubhouse! Home features open floor plan, 1500+ SQFT, 2 bdrm, 2 bath and an extra office/den area! Kitchen includes modern design touches with eating space, all appliances included, dining room, pantry, walk in utility and plenty of storage. Spacious Primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet, large bathroom with extra-large shower and double vanity. Home features a large private lot, fully fenced, gated entry, Hardi board siding, large covered front deck, outbuilding for storage, RV parking, dead end street for less traffic and fire pit! Amenities include pool, park, clubhouse and Saltwater access. Don't miss out on this 2017 affordable home!
